milestones.description: Mike Brearley has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs, going past Dayle Hadlee's 3
Wasim Bari has broken the record for most dismissals (27) in ODIs, going past Rod Marsh's 25
Wasim Raja has broken the record for most catches (8) in ODIs for PAK, going past Zaheer Abbas's 7
England's 15-run win against Pakistan is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 19-run win against New Zealand
Bob Willis and Bob Taylor's 43-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 40 between Underwood and Bob Taylor
Wasim Bari and Imran Khan's 30-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 27 between Wasim Bari and Sarfraz Nawaz
